        "action": "Ban chat functions in Apps used by children under 13 yrs old",
        "additional_details": "Preventing access to chat functions would keep children safer online, saving police/social services time and money.\r\n \r\nhttps://www.barnardos.org.uk/news/press_releases.htm?ref=131168 \r\n \r\nhttps://www.nspcc.org.uk/preventing-abuse/child-abuse-and-neglect/child-sexual-exploitation/",
